description:
Amadou &amp; Mariam - 1990-1995: Le Meilleur Des Annees Maliennes
2005

Released in English-speaking countries as
1990-1995 The Best Of The African Years

Brought to you by TQMP
The Quality Music Project

In 1998, Amadou &amp; Mariam released their first album Sou Ni Tile. The first record was anticipating their successful 2nd album Dimanche A Bamako. 7 years later, it's time to come back on their very first beginnings: in West Africa. This compilation includes 16 previously unreleased recordings from the two albums.
--- amazon.com

